summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit to condemn land and other property for the laying off, widening, altering and establishing of North 51st Street, North 52nd Street and North 54th Street, each from Interlaken Avenue to Woodlawn Avenue, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 21047, Cause No. 78442, in so far as the same affects lots 1 to 4, inclusive, block 10, in Wallingford's Division of Green Lake Addition to the City of Seattle.
